 "<p>These transform the <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span>, <span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span> and <span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span> vectors. </p>\n": "<p>\u8fd9\u4e9b\u53d8\u6362<span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span>\u3001<span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span>\u548c<span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span>\u5411\u91cf\u3002</p>\n",
